title: Malcolm Turnbull takes new approach to Question Time
text: The Abbott era has been over for more than a month and there is more evidence of a fresh approach. The former treasurer Joe Hockey's confirmed he's heading out the door for good at the end of this week, and Malcolm Turnbull's announced that after this week backbenchers will get more scope to ask questions about issues in their electorates. Labor's tried to use Question Time to reveal how little has changed - but Mr Turnbull's accused them of being unable to break out of the old dying political discourse. ...
